# SpectralBridge Project Context

## Project Overview
Building SpectralBridge: frequency-aware audio-visual alignment beyond CLIP.
Master's application portfolio for Koç University.

## Current Phase
Week 1: Investigating datasets (Loie/VGGSound on HuggingFace vs manual download)

## Tech Stack
- PyTorch, transformers, timm
- BEATs + DINOv2 (self-supervised encoders)
- Target: Google Colab T4 GPU

## Project Structure
src/ - reusable modules
scripts/ - standalone scripts
notebooks/ - Colab notebooks
configs/ - YAML configs

## Coding Style
- Type hints, docstrings
- Small focused functions
- Cache everything to avoid recomputation
